  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MessageReceiver
    Provides the basic interface implemented by all classes receiving messages of any type in the DESMO-J framework.
    OutputType
    Interface for all Outputs (Report, Trace, Error, Debug) in format like HTML, ASCII, XML written line by line.
    OutputTypeEndToExport
    Interface for Outputs that cannot be written line by line, e.g.
    TableFormatter
    An interface representing basic facilites for writing data into tables.
